providing a central evaluating facility communicatively connected to participants' locations and to said playback facility having comparing means programmable to recognize and-accept an acceptable answer and having means for identifying individual participants who have entered an acceptable answer within the allowed time period; 
programming said comparing means; 
evaluating a participant's entered answer received at said evaluation facility; 
identifying participants who have entered an acceptable answer; 
providing a central informing facility for playing back a second recording to inform participants who have entered an acceptable answer, the playing back of said second recording being automatically initiated by the acceptance of a participant's entered answer; and 
informing participants who have entered an acceptable answer; 
wherein said evaluation facility evaluates an individual answer essentially immediately following its input by a participant; and 
