a central tamper-resisting data storage facility; 
a facility at a central location for determining a task and response criteria defining at least one acceptable response to said task, said response criteria including a rating scale for acceptable responses; 
a plurality of remote playing stations for players, including means at each playing station for entering response data by individual players; 
first communication means for transmitting task data from a central location to players' stations; 
second communication means for transmitting instructional signals conveying response criteria data from a central location to said tamper-resisting data storage facility; 
third communication means for transmitting a player's entered response data to said data storage facility; 
means for identifying players having entered a response; 
means operatively connected to said data storage facility and responsive to instructional signals for comparing a player's entered response data to acceptable response data to determine a player's acceptable entered response and its rating; 
means for comparing the ratings of players having entered acceptable responses to each other to determine a relative standing of players; 
means for preventing the comparing of a player's entered response following a predetermined point in time; and 
means for informing identified players of their relative standings; 
wherein said task comprises at least one question which is either a single-part question or a multiple-part question; and 
wherein an acceptable response has been determined prior to communicating task data to players' stations.

