means at remote locations for receiving signals conveying said outcome criteria and said award; 
means at remote locations operable by a participant for entering data indicating a decision about the event and comprising means for authorizing a central account maintenance facility to debit a participant's account for participant's participation; 
central means for electronically transmitting signals conveying event outcome information to remote locations and to central evaluation means; 
a central evaluation sub-system comprising: 
means for receiving a participant's entered decision; 
means for identifying participants having entered a decision; 
means for receiving outcome criteria; and 
means for evaluating participants' entered decision, including means for comparing individual participants' entered decisions to event outcome information on the basis of outcome criteria and including means for determining an award for an acceptable decision based on outcome criteria; 
means for crediting a successful participant's account with a central amount maintenance facility with said award; and 
means for informing a successful participant of said award.

